  Ho5 Hia tan2 Goa2. <BR>Hia tan2 Goa2. <BR>Hia u7 Oah8-mia7 e5 chhiu7 teh khui, <BR>Hia tan2 Goa2. <BR>Si2-sit, kau3-be2 bo5 koan5-se3, <BR>Ti7 hit-peng5 si7 lan2 chou2-ke; <BR>Seng3-tou5 kau3 hia kiN3 ThiN Pe7, <BR>Hia tan2 Goa2. 
